          <ul class="text-[var(--muted)] leading-relaxed space-y-2 list-disc pl-5">
            <li><strong>Third-Party Services and Products.</strong> Issues resulting from Third-Party Platforms or products not directly supplied or controlled by Wyre Technology, including outages, API changes, discontinuation of services, changes in terms of service, or access restrictions imposed by those platforms.</li>
            <li><strong>Your Actions and Tool Calls.</strong> Any data created, modified, deleted, or otherwise affected on Third-Party Platforms as a result of Tool Calls executed through the Service on your behalf, whether initiated by you directly or by an AI assistant acting on your instructions.</li>
            <li><strong>Failure to Follow Recommendations.</strong> Failures or performance issues resulting from your disregard for recommendations, instructions, or best practices provided by Wyre Technology, including but not limited to recommendations to use read-only API keys or to review AI outputs before acting on them.</li>
