          <ul class="text-[var(--muted)] leading-relaxed space-y-2 list-disc pl-5 mb-3">
            <li>Loss, corruption, deletion, or unauthorized modification of data on any Third-Party Platform resulting from Tool Calls executed through the Service;</li>
            <li>AI hallucinations, inaccuracies, or fabricated outputs;</li>
            <li>Unpredictable or unintended AI behavior, including unintended Tool Calls;</li>
            <li>Actions taken by AI assistants on Third-Party Platforms using your credentials;</li>
            <li>Failures, outages, API changes, or discontinuation of Third-Party Platforms;</li>
            <li>Your failure to review and validate AI-generated outputs or Tool Call results before relying on them;</li>
            <li>Loss of revenue, profits, business, or data.</li>
          </ul>
          <p class="text-[var(--muted)] leading-relaxed">
            Our total aggregate liability to you for any and all claims arising out of or related to these Terms or the Service shall not exceed the amount you paid for the Service in the three (3) months preceding the claim.
          </p>
        </section>

        <section>
