          <p class="text-[var(--muted)] leading-relaxed mb-3">
            You agree to indemnify, defend, and hold harmless Wyre Technology and its officers, directors, employees, and agents from and against any and all claims, damages, losses, liabilities, costs, and expenses (including reasonable attorneys' fees) arising from or related to:
